  m_text: "Well, well... it seems you actually listened to me. The mess is gone,
    the trash is in the sink, and my room is finally clean. I am a ghost of my word
    \u2014 the doors are now unlocked. You are free to leave... for now. Run along
    before I change my mind!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
